パッケージ xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator

クラス AdvancementFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator.AdvancementFactory
  • public class AdvancementFactory
extends Object
    A class containing methods which should drastically speed up the creation of the common advancements. Also offers auto-activation functionalities.

    • コンストラクタの詳細

      • AdvancementFactory

        public AdvancementFactory​(org.bukkit.plugin.Plugin plugin,
                          boolean autoActivate,
                          boolean autoReload)
        パラメータ:
        plugin - the advancements' ids will be created in this plugin's namespace
        autoActivate - whether the advancement should be automatically activated directly after creation
        autoReload - whether Bukkit.reloadData() should be called immediately after an advancement has been created. autoActivate mustn't be false if this is true

    • メソッドの詳細

      • getSimple

        public Advancement getSimple​(String id,
                             @Nullable
                             @Nullable Advancement parent,
                             String title,
                             String description,
                             MaterialId icon,
                             int data,
                             String triggerId,
                             Trigger trigger)
        Creates a new Advancement with the specified contents and possibly activates it (and possibly calls Bukkit.reloadData()) depending on the parameters passed in the constructor.
        パラメータ:
        id - the id of the advancement, without namespace
        parent - the parent advancement, can be null. getRoot(String, String, String, MaterialId, int, String) may be more suitable for root advancements
        title - the title of the advancement
        description - the description of the advancement
        icon - the icon of the advancement
        data - the icon's data value
        triggerId - the id of the trigger
        trigger - the trigger of the advancement
        戻り値:
        the created advancement

      • getAll

        public <T> Advancement getAll​(String id,
                              @Nullable
                              @Nullable Advancement parent,
                              String title,
                              String description,
                              MaterialId icon,
                              int data,
                              T[] contents,
                              Function<T,​Trigger> triggerCreator)
        Similar to getSimple(String, Advancement, String, String, MaterialId, int, String, Trigger), but this method adds multiple triggers, all of which must be completed in order to complete the advancement. The triggers are generated by iterating over the contents array and calling the triggerCreator function.
